-- Egypt, China May Form Joint Oil and Gas Services Company, Ahram Reports
-- Ola Galal
-- 2010-09-07T06:20:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/egypt-china-may-form-a-joint-oil-gas-services-company-al-ahram-reports.html

          
          
             Egypt and China are studying setting
up a joint company for oil and gas services to operate in Africa
and the Middle East,  Al Ahram  reported, citing Egyptian Oil
Minister  Sameh Fahmy .  
